-\pi < Arg(z) \leq \pi
\arg(z) = Arg(z) + 2 \pi K
K \in \mathbb{Z}
z = -2-2i \Rightarrow r=|z|=\sqrt{4+4}=2\sqrt{2} \Rightarrow z = 2\sqrt{2} (-\frac{2}{2\sqrt{2}}-\frac{2i}{2\sqrt{2}}) = 2\sqrt{2} (-\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}-\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2} i) 
\Rightarrow \theta = \frac{5\pi}{4}-2\pi = -\frac{3\pi}{4}
